:c.Decimal (floating-point)
:row split=yes.
:c.:pk.%lf:epk.
:c.:pk.double:epk.
:c.Long decimal (floating-point)
:row split=yes.
:c.:pk.%c:epk.
:c.:pk.char:epk.
:c.Single character
:row split=yes.
:c.:pk.%s:epk.
:c.:pk.char*:epk.
:c.Multiple characters (string)
:row split=yes.
:c.:pk.%p:epk.
:c.:pk.void*:epk.
:c.Memory address as hexadecimal
:row split=yes.
:c.:pk.%x:epk. or :pk.%X:epk.
